<div class="banner">
  <h1> Surviving Finals </h1>
</div>

<p>
To survive finals with good grades and a reasonable mental state you need to learn how. The main ideas that are the most important are stress management, test taking, study strategies, time management, and decision making. The table below gives one solution to each of these main ideas. Below the table there is more specific information that provides several strategies and how one might implement those strategies. 
</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <td>Promblem</td>
      <td>One Solution</td>
      <td>Image</td>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tr>
    <td>Stress</td>
    <td>Take a break from the stressor</td>
    <td><img src="http://www.hhblife.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/hhblife-ways-to-relieve-stress.jpg"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
